                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1306&quot; title=&quot;LBUG at (dlm_lock.c:213:ldlm_lock_add_to_lru_nolock()) ASSERTION(lock-&amp;gt;l_resource-&amp;gt;lr_type != LDLM_FLOCK failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1306&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1306&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was ported into 1.8 and there were no updates from WC about landing this patch last 3 months.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like nobody cares about &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1306&quot; title=&quot;LBUG at (dlm_lock.c:213:ldlm_lock_add_to_lru_nolock()) ASSERTION(lock-&amp;gt;l_resource-&amp;gt;lr_type != LDLM_FLOCK failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1306&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1306&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; since it&apos;s in &quot;resolved&quot; state.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please, commit the patch into 1.8 also.&lt;br/&gt;
Here is updated version for 1.8:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Andriy Skulysh added a comment - 14/May/12 5:33 AM&lt;br/&gt;
patch for b1_8: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/2727&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/2727&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;thanks a lot!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
